  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK470">
<l>eḷḷāta veṇṇic ceyalvēṇṭun tammoṭu</l>
<l>koḷḷāta koḷḷā tulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let a man reflect, and do things which bring no reproach; the world will not approve, with him, of things which do not become of his position to adopt.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
